	 (3 . ,SEMI-SHARP) (0 . ,SEMI-SHARP) (4 . ,SEMI-SHARP) (1 . ,SEMI-SHARP)
	 (5 . ,SEMI-SHARP) (2 . ,SEMI-SHARP) (6 . ,SEMI-SHARP)
